<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">

    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile_pic.png",
        width: 250, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div
              class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
              role="progressbar"
              aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
              aria-valuemax="100"
              style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
              >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>My name is Sergio Aravena Jr. and I've been passionate about technology for as long as I can remember. I grew up watching
        Star Wars, The Matrix and Star Trek wondering when will all this be a reality? Now, I've decided to help create it one application
        at a time!</p>

        <p>However, my path to software development wasn't a conventional one. I worked for the Federal Government for approximately
        15 years before fully committing to my dreams of being a developer. I attended a full-stack web developer bootcamp in my hometown of
        Miami, FL and was instantly hooked! Now I take on projects, and am currently starting my own technology
        startup.</p>

        <p>
          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#jobHistory"
          name="button"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#education"
          name="button"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controller="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Full Stack Web Developer and Aspiring Tech Entrepreneur
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block">
              Federal Agent - US Department of Homeland Security
              08/2010 - 8/2017
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block">
              Inspector - US Department of Homeland Security
              11/2002 - 08/2010
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Wyncode Academy - Immersive Full Stack Web Developer Bootcamp
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block">
              Florida International University - Bachelors in Business Administration
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
